<text><body>
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0742.0548c" n="0548c"/>
<lb n="0548c01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0548c02"/><head type="no">No. 742</head>
<lb n="0548c03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title><note n="0548052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0548052"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>自愛經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0548c04"/>
<lb n="0548c05"/><byline type="Translator">東晉<note n="0548053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天竺三藏＝西域沙門【三】【宮】</note><note n="0548053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天竺三藏＝西域沙門【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0548053"><lem>天竺三藏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">西域沙門</rdg></app>竺曇無蘭譯</byline>
<lb n="0548c06"/><div1 type="jing"><p>聞如是。一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。時
<lb n="0548c07"/>國王詣佛所。遙見精舍。下車&CB00230;蓋解劍脫履。
<lb n="0548c08"/>拱手直進。五體投地。稽首足下。&CB00230;長跪<note n="0548054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">白＝曰【三】【宮】</note><note n="0548054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">白＝曰【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0548054"><lem>白</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">曰</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0548c09"/>願以來日。於四街道請佛及<note n="0548055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（眾）＋僧【三】【宮】</note><note n="0548055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（眾）＋僧【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0548055"><lem>僧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">眾僧</rdg></app>。施設微食。
<lb n="0548c10"/>普令愚民知佛至尊。&CB00418;其儀式傳世為則。願
<lb n="0548c11"/>使眾生遠鬼妖蠱。悉奉五戒。以<note n="0548056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">消＝銷【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0548056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">消＝銷【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0548056"><lem>消</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">銷</rdg></app>國患。世
<lb n="0548c12"/>尊曰。善哉善哉。夫為國王。宜有明導率民。以
<lb n="0548c13"/>道請求來福。吾昔為王。亦奉<note n="0548057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸＝請【三】【宮】</note><note n="0548057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸＝請【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0548057"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">請</rdg></app>佛沙門梵
<lb n="0548c14"/>志。常行四等六度。勤以致佛巍巍無上。</p>
<lb n="0548c15"/><p>王曰。至真誠如佛教。夫不種<note n="0548058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">核＝栽【元】【明】</note><app n="0548058"><lem>核</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">栽</rdg></app>無緣獲其
<lb n="0548c16"/>果。吾受佛恩生世為人。去女即男六情完具。
<lb n="0548c17"/>景福之會值佛處世。盛明法化在於吾國。積
<lb n="0548c18"/>善難量乞退嚴辦。世尊曰。善哉善哉。王即還
<lb n="0548c19"/>宮。平治大道高下齊平。廣設帳幔&CB00594;諸幢幡。
<lb n="0548c20"/>自彼四衢至精舍門。<note n="0548059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">挾＝俠【宋】【宮】，夾【明】</note><note n="0548059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">挾＝俠【宋】【宮】，＝夾【明】</note><app n="0548059"><lem>挾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">俠</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">夾</rdg></app>道欄楯羅燈如星。步
<lb n="0548c21"/>有香爐。天樂眾伎歌佛至尊之靈。諮嗟沙門
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0742.0549a" n="0549a"/>
<lb n="0549a01"/>清貞之德。散華雜寶紛紛如雨。香湯灑地。&CB00230;
<lb n="0549a02"/>敷綩綖。王親通夜手自為饌。身往奉迎稽首
<lb n="0549a03"/>于地。長跪曰。願世尊。垂大慈現影則濟眾生。
<lb n="0549a04"/>佛起著法服。與諸沙門俱之四衢。王及群臣
<lb n="0549a05"/>翼從左右。佛至就座。夫人太子皆稽首于地。
<lb n="0549a06"/>攘衣跣<note n="0549001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02303;＝襪【宋】【元】，&CB10483;【宮】</note><note n="0549001" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">&CB02594;</lem><rdg wit="【大】">&CB02303;</rdg></app>＝襪【宋】【元】，＝&CB10483;【宮】</note><app n="0549001"><lem>&CB02594;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">襪</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&CB10483;</rdg></app>。行澡水已。手自斟酌。佛飯畢稽
<lb n="0549a07"/>首曰。今設微食。願天人鬼龍<note n="0549002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蜎＝蠉【宮】</note><app n="0549002"><lem>蜎</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">蠉</rdg></app>蜚蚑行蠕動
<lb n="0549a08"/>之類。令世世逢佛逢法逢沙門眾。去<note n="0549003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世＝諸【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世＝諸【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549003"><lem>世</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">諸</rdg></app>穢
<lb n="0549a09"/><note n="0549004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">臊＝邪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">臊＝邪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549004"><lem>臊</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">邪</rdg></app>懷佛正真。佛言。善哉。王為民父母。潤之
<lb n="0549a10"/>以慈。導以大明。所願必得。王曰。普地之民當
<lb n="0549a11"/>別之際。咸曰自愛。自愛之<note n="0549005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">義＝議【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">義＝議【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549005"><lem>義</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">議</rdg></app>其有要乎。</p>
<lb n="0549a12"/><p>世尊歎曰。善哉問也。夫人處世。心懷毒念。口
<lb n="0549a13"/>施毒言。身行毒業。斯三事出<note n="0549006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">于＝乎【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0549006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">于＝乎【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0549006"><lem>于</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">乎</rdg></app>心身口。唱
<lb n="0549a14"/>成其惡。<note n="0549007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549007"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>加眾生。眾生被毒即結怨恨。誓
<lb n="0549a15"/>心欲報。或現世<note n="0549008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">獲＋（願）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">獲＋（願）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549008"><lem>獲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">獲願</rdg></app>。或身終後魂靈昇天即下
<lb n="0549a16"/>報之。人中畜生鬼神太山。更相剋賊。皆由宿
<lb n="0549a17"/>命。非空生也。身三口四意三無惡。愚者恣之。
<lb n="0549a18"/>不孝其親。敬奉鬼妖。婬亂酒悖。就下賤之濁。
<lb n="0549a19"/>以致危身滅族之禍。死入太山湯火之酷。長
<lb n="0549a20"/>不獲人身。去佛遠<note n="0549009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">正＝政【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0549009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">正＝政【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0549009"><lem>正</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">政</rdg></app>不樂沙門之清戒。常與
<lb n="0549a21"/>愚會。斯謂樂危亡之禍。不自愛者也。王曰。
<lb n="0549a22"/><note n="0549010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善善＝善哉善哉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善善＝善哉善哉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549010"><lem>善善</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">善哉善哉</rdg></app><note n="0549011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0549011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0549011"><lem>唯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>佛教誡。願聞自愛。其則云何。</p>
<lb n="0549a23"/><p>佛言。自愛之法。先三自歸。以法養親。慈愛人
<lb n="0549a24"/>物。悲愍愚惑。見<app type="＊" source="0549009"><lem>正</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">政</rdg></app>喜進。平等普護。安濟眾
<lb n="0549a25"/>生。<note n="0549012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">施斯＝斯施【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">施斯＝斯施【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549012"><lem>施斯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">斯施</rdg></app>四恩。布施窮乏。眾生無怨。諸天祐
<lb n="0549a26"/>育眾橫不加。牢獄利劍諸毒<app type="＊" source="0548056"><lem>消</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">銷</rdg></app>歇。親安族
<lb n="0549a27"/>興。生無災患死得上天。常與明會。斯謂自愛
<lb n="0549a28"/>者也。王曰。善哉。<app type="＊" source="0549011"><lem>唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惟</rdg></app>佛教誡。誠高行賢者。清
<lb n="0549a29"/>貞守真。穢利邪樂不以染心。口四不言。三凶
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0742.0549b" n="0549b"/>
<lb n="0549b01"/>遠身。危命全行諸佛所珍。<note n="0549013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">親＝&CB13544;【宋】</note><app n="0549013"><lem>親</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&CB13544;</rdg></app>安族興終得
<lb n="0549b02"/>上天常得福會。斯謂自愛者也。王曰。善哉。
<lb n="0549b03"/><app type="＊" source="0549011"><lem>唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惟</rdg></app>佛教真。眾<note n="0549014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">毒＝恚【元】【明】</note><app n="0549014"><lem>毒</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">恚</rdg></app>橫加。忍默不說。慈惻愍彼。
<lb n="0549b04"/>終始濟之。精進不怠。紹心三尊。外靜內寂
<lb n="0549b05"/><note n="0549015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">殖＝植【三】，值【宮】</note><note n="0549015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">殖＝植【宋】【元】【明】，＝值【宮】</note><app n="0549015"><lem>殖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">植</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">值</rdg></app>念道根。深觀聖趣。明化真言。孝親濟已。
<lb n="0549b06"/>導眾使然。常與福會。<note n="0549016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔斯〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔斯〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549016"><lem>斯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>謂自愛者也。王曰。
<lb n="0549b07"/>善哉<app type="＊" source="0549011"><lem>唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惟</rdg></app>佛教真觀者無數。時有兩商人。一人
<lb n="0549b08"/>念曰。佛身丈六華色紫金。頂有肉髻。項有
<lb n="0549b09"/><note n="0549017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">日＝白【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">日＝白【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549017"><lem>日</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">白</rdg></app>光。巍巍難言。佛如帝王。沙門猶忠臣。佛
<lb n="0549b10"/>陳明法。沙門誦宣。斯王明矣。知佛可尊。佛知
<lb n="0549b11"/>其念熟視之。其人心喜喜如獲寶。其一人念
<lb n="0549b12"/>曰。斯王愚惑。爾為國<note n="0549018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">主＝王【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">主＝王【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549018"><lem>主</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">王</rdg></app>將復何求。佛者若
<lb n="0549b13"/>牛。弟子猶車。彼牛牽車東西南北。佛亦猶然。
<lb n="0549b14"/>子有何道屈意奉之乎。佛知其有惡念必獲
<lb n="0549b15"/>其殃。愴然愍之。其人心懼。若有所遭。二人俱
<lb n="0549b16"/>去。<note n="0549019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝四【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0549019"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">四</rdg></app>十里<note n="0549020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">停＝亭【元】【明】</note><app n="0549020"><lem>停</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">亭</rdg></app>宿<note n="0549021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沽＝酤【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沽＝酤【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549021"><lem>沽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">酤</rdg></app>酒飲之共平。屬事訟之
<lb n="0549b17"/>紛<note n="0549022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">紛＝紜【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">紛＝紜【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549022"><lem>紛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">紜</rdg></app>。其善念者。四王遣善神護焉。毒<note n="0549023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心＝念【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心＝念【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549023"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">念</rdg></app>謗
<lb n="0549b18"/>佛者。太山鬼令酒入<note n="0549024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">腸＝腹【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">腸＝腹【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549024"><lem>腸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">腹</rdg></app>。猶火燒身。出<note n="0549025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">停＝亭【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">停＝亭【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549025"><lem>停</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">亭</rdg></app>路
<lb n="0549b19"/>臥。即宛轉落車轍中。晨有商人。車五百乘轢
<lb n="0549b20"/>殺之焉。伴求而見。其然曰吾衰矣還國見。
<lb n="0549b21"/>疑取物去為不義。遂輕身委財而逝。展轉遠
<lb n="0549b22"/>邁。去舍衛數萬里。有一國。國王崩無太子。讖
<lb n="0549b23"/>書云。中土有微人。當王斯土。群僚議曰。國之
<lb n="0549b24"/>無君。猶體之無首。難以久立也。故王有馬。常
<lb n="0549b25"/>為王禮。若有任王者馬必屈膝。<note n="0549026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">僉＝命【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">僉＝命【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549026"><lem>僉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">命</rdg></app>曰大善。
<lb n="0549b26"/>即具嚴駕。以王印綬著車上。人馬填路。觀者
<lb n="0549b27"/>莫不<note n="0549027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">揮＝麾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">揮＝麾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549027"><lem>揮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">麾</rdg></app>涕。商人亦出觀。國太史曰。彼有黃
<lb n="0549b28"/>雲之蓋。斯者氣也。神馬直進屈膝舐商人足。
<lb n="0549b29"/>群臣欣豫香湯澡浴。拜為國王僉然稱臣。王
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0742.0549c" n="0549c"/>
<lb n="0549c01"/>曰。余本商人無德於民。不任天位也。群僚曰。
<lb n="0549c02"/>天授有德神馬屈膝。於是遂處王宮。聽省國
<lb n="0549c03"/>政。深惟曰。余無微善。何緣獲此。必是佛恩使
<lb n="0549c04"/>之然也。晨在御座歎佛無上之聖。率諸群僚
<lb n="0549c05"/>向<note n="0549028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">舍衛＝佛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">舍衛＝佛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549028"><lem>舍衛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">佛</rdg></app>稽首曰。賤人蒙世尊潤獲為人王。斯
<lb n="0549c06"/>土傳世不知有佛。流俗之書亦無記焉。願以
<lb n="0549c07"/>大明。開斯國人之聾盲。明日願與應真<note n="0549029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">眾＋（聖）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眾＋（聖）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549029"><lem>眾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">眾聖</rdg></app>
<lb n="0549c08"/>垂意顧斯一時三月。佛告阿難。&CB00330;諸比丘。明
<lb n="0549c09"/>日彼王請。皆當徐徐變化現神尊德。令其國
<lb n="0549c10"/>民咸共&CB00418;焉。諸天聞佛至彼教化。相率導從。
<lb n="0549c11"/>作樂歌德。寶帳幢幡。華下紛紛。光色耀人。佛
<lb n="0549c12"/>及應真皆坐正殿。王案舍衛國王供養明法。
<lb n="0549c13"/><note n="0549030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">身＝手【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">身＝手【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549030"><lem>身</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">手</rdg></app>自斟酌。畢以小<note n="0549031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">机＝凡【宋】，几【元】【明】【宮】</note><note n="0549031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">机＝凡【宋】，＝几【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549031"><lem>机</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">凡</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">几</rdg></app>於佛前坐。佛廣說法。
<lb n="0549c14"/>王曰。吾本微人素無快德。何緣獲斯。佛告
<lb n="0549c15"/>王<note n="0549032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔曰〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔曰〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549032"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。昔彼王飯佛。王心念言。佛如國王。沙
<lb n="0549c16"/>門猶臣下。王種斯栽。今自獲其果。彼一人云。
<lb n="0549c17"/>佛若牛弟子如車。彼自種車轢之栽。今在太
<lb n="0549c18"/>山為火車所轢。自獲其果也。非王勇健所能
<lb n="0549c19"/>致矣。為善福隨。履惡禍追。響之應聲。善惡如
<lb n="0549c20"/>音。非天龍鬼神所為。非先靈所為。造之者心
<lb n="0549c21"/>成身口矣。佛說偈<note n="0549033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曰＝言【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曰＝言【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549033"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">言</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0549c22"/><lg><l>心為法本</l><l>心尊心使</l><l>中心<note n="0549034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">作＝念【元】【明】</note><app n="0549034"><lem>作</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">念</rdg></app>惡</l>
<lb n="0549c23"/><l>即言即行</l><l>罪苦自追</l><l>車轢<app type="＊" source="0549006"><lem>于</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">乎</rdg></app>轍</l>
<lb n="0549c24"/><l>心為法本</l><l>心尊心使</l><l>中心念善</l>
<lb n="0549c25"/><l>即言即行</l><l>福樂自追</l><l>如影隨形</l></lg>
<lb n="0549c26"/><p>世尊又告王曰。眾惡之罪最重有五。不孝不
<lb n="0549c27"/>忠殺親殺君。家滅國亂。重<note n="0549035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">罪＝羅【元】</note><app n="0549035"><lem>罪</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app>一也。<note n="0549036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝罪【宋】【元】</note><app n="0549036"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">罪</rdg></app>漢之
<lb n="0549c28"/>行<note n="0549037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得＝德【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0549037"><lem>得</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">德</rdg></app>空不願無<note n="0549038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">想＝相【三】【宮】</note><note n="0549038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">想＝相【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0549038"><lem>想</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">相</rdg></app>之定。與佛齊意拯濟眾
<lb n="0549c29"/>生。而愚向之。重罪二也。佛者眾罪已畢。景福
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0742.0550a" n="0550a"/>
<lb n="0550a01"/>會成。相好十力法導眾生。慈悲喜護心過慈
<lb n="0550a02"/>母。而愚惡謗。重罪三也。清<note n="0550001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淨＝潔【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">淨＝潔【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550001"><lem>淨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">潔</rdg></app>沙門志清行
<lb n="0550a03"/>高。懷抱經法助佛化愚。諸佛相紹繼眾生得
<lb n="0550a04"/>度。皆由眾僧。佞讒交<note n="0550002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">搆＝遘【宋】【元】【宮】，構【明】</note><note n="0550002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">搆＝遘【宋】【元】【宮】，＝構【明】</note><app n="0550002"><lem>搆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">遘</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">構</rdg></app>以致不調。僧不調
<lb n="0550a05"/><note n="0550003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">政＝正【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0550003"><lem>政</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">正</rdg></app>法毀民狂走。<app type="＊" source="0550003"><lem>政</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">正</rdg></app>法毀民狂走者。三道興
<lb n="0550a06"/>惱比丘僧。重罪四也。佛之尊廟寶物水土。眾
<lb n="0550a07"/>生赤心以貢三尊。愚人或毀盜之。重罪<note n="0550004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">五＋（者）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">五＋（者）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550004"><lem>五</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">五者</rdg></app>
<lb n="0550a08"/>也。犯斯五者。<note n="0550005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">罪無請＝其罪最重【元】【明】</note><app n="0550005"><lem>罪無請</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">其罪最重</rdg></app>。謂<note n="0550006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔之〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550006"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>自殺身自滅族
<lb n="0550a09"/>自投太山火矣。五罪之重重於須彌。慎無犯
<lb n="0550a10"/>焉。佛說經竟。王及群臣皆得須陀洹。受五戒
<lb n="0550a11"/>為清信士。國民有作沙門者。守戒為清信士
<lb n="0550a12"/>者。遂以五戒十善為國政。諸天祐護國遂興
<lb n="0550a13"/>矣。諸天龍神王臣黎民。無不歡喜。</p></div1>
